title: Spiller emerges in Saints' 26-20 OT win over Cowboys
text:
> Sports Spiller emerges in Saints' 26-20 OT win over Cowboys New Orleans Saints running back C.J. Spiller (28) scores the game-winning touchdown during overtime of an NFL football game against the Dallas Cowboys in New Orleans, Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015. The Saints won 26-20. (AP Photo/Jonathan Bachman)
